title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Anandi and Jagdish attend their final exams.Meanwhile, Dadisa buys jewellery for Nandu, Gehna and Sumitra. But, Basant tries to explain Gehna that they are dependent on Dadisa's money.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Basant Singh is irritated with himself. Anandi gets scolded by Kalyani Devi. Khajaan Singh leaves his home, even after knowing Anandi and her in laws are coming.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Jagdish gets upset when he cannot not find Anandi at home. Anandi's father reacts rudely when she mentions Dadisa's name.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Anandi wants to go the field with her father but he refuses saying that he has some important work to do. She gets yelled at by her father when she asks about the boxes of ghee in the godown.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Khajaan Singh refuses to go along with Anandi and Bhago due to which Anandi gets upset. Dadisa doubts Khajaan's wealth and sarcastically asks Bhago about it.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Jagdish secures the first rank in the class and everyone congratulates him. Anandi is sad as she is not satisfied with her marks. Dadiji plans a surprise for Jagdish.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Bhairon gifts Jagdish a mobile phone. Everyone enjoys the moment. Teachers tell Bhairon that Jagdish has just managed to pass in his exams. On hearing this Bhairon slaps Jagdish.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Jagdish apologizes for his mistake to everyone. Jagdish meets his friend Hariya and plans to go to Mumbai without informing anyone. Bhairon reads out the letter and everyone gets tensed.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Jagdish's family is worried. Jagdish and Hariya reach Mumbai. They are in trouble when they get separated. Jagdish is caught by a mugger. Anandi finds Jagdish's letter and phone.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Jagdish and Hariya tour Mumbai. Jagdish calls Anandi. Anandi betrays the promise and informs the family. Bhairon tracks Jagdish's location. Everybody is shocked to know that Jagya is in Mumbai.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Anandi and others reach Mumbai to look for Jagdish. Jagdish and Hariya are kidnapped. Jagdish sees Anandi in a taxi. He struggles to call her, but his effort goes in vain.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Bhairon Singh regrets scolding Jagdish, as Jagdish runs away from home. He is later kidnapped and he fears the thugs, as they desire to turn him into a physically handicapped person.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Sumitra grieves at losing Jagdish and Daadisa consoles her. Bairon begins his search for Jagdish. Later, Jagdish manages to notify Anandi about his location, but fears getting caught with the cell phone.
